{
  "stem": "10588.8",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know whether this fits in, but anyhow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He asked me if I knew a girl, Manya [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I knew her by sight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I didn't know too much about anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I said, yeah, I know who she is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I said, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So he told me that her brother's told me that he has a sister here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I said, you should go and see her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my girlfriend is doing like this to my arm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "What, do you send a cat for butter?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You sending him to another girl?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You like him?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I-- I do-- I insist he's going to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So Bina would not permit him to go alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She sent Mendel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He said, now we can engaged.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that was-- I met him June 24, 1964.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "July 1, we were engaged.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "What year?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1964, the same year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And July 3, we were married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1964.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So from June 24, you know, just-- and-- and the funny point is, I never had a honeymoon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I say somebody want me to hear about the honeymoon, everybody looks at me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What kind of crazy woman talk-- tells about her honeymoon?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It must have been like 18 days or something like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't count the days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But from June 20-- 26-- 26, I think, or 24 or 26, till July the 13th.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After July 1, I was engaged already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- 1964. 1946!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- because-- I-- 1946. 19-- 19-- in-- in 1945, we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was in 1946.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- what-- then what we did, Mendel had an apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came both, and they got a little apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a little apartment, so we switched.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
